50|$|The series EN 50436 {{specifies}} {{the test}} procedures and basic performance requirements for <b>alcohol</b> <b>interlocks</b> and gives guidance to authorities, decision makers, purchasers and users. Additionally, it describes {{the requirements for}} vehicles for the installation <b>alcohol</b> <b>interlocks.</b>|$|R
